"1 1/2 tablespoons balsamic vinegar","1 tablespoon extra-virgin olive oil","1 1/2 teaspoons lemon juice","1  clove garlic, minced","1/8 teaspoon celery seed","  Pinch black pepper","1/2 cup rinsed and drained canned lentils","1  plum tomato, diced","1/4  small red onion, diced (about 1/4 cup)","1/4  yellow bell pepper, seeded and diced (about 1/4 cup)","3  fresh basil leaves, chopped (about 1 Tbsp.)","3  to 4 Bibb lettuce leaves","1/2 cup cooked quinoa, cold"